'''Ɛbdullah Acini'''  ({{Tifinaɣ | '''ⵄⴱⴷⵓⵍⵍⴰⵀ ⴰⵛⵉⵏⵉ'''}}) ia yan unazur [[amaziɣ]] imqqurn ilul ɣ usas ɣ tamazirt n [[Libya]], ia '''Ɛbdullah Acini''' yan itmaɣn f [[tutlayt]] [[tamaziɣt]] isffaɣd tuut n tisfifin isawaln f tamait. Ɣilad illa ɣ ubniq ɣ [[libya]] tiira lliɣ yixs ɣ yan unmuqqar n uzawan ɣ tamazirt n [[tizirin tiknariyin|Tizirin Tiknariyin]]. 

Tlla trabbut ad ɣ iɣerm n Zwara da ituyssanen er imezdaɣen nes s wassaɣ n "Tamurt". Yusi εabdullah εcini d ayt trabbut nes, anezum n tutlayt d idels amaziɣ, ar tiriren s tutlayt tamaziɣt mqar tt idel usennaraf (dictateur) alibi. 

Iɣra εcini aẓawan, iwattes ad isers tiɣri d tarmit nes  ubrid n usmaynu n umar d [[Azawan|Uzawan]] amaziɣ alibi. 

Tesmun "Ussan" iεerrimen imaziɣen da irban anezum d tiwariwin am : εli Fṭis, εabd Rauf Bunduq, εimad Lɣamisi, Ramzi Lɣali, Ḥasaniya Leεzabi d εliyin Salem. Tiwes terabbut Ussan  unmuar n Tafswit  [[Dzayr]]  [[2004]], d anmuar amaḍlan n uẓawan amazih  [[Tizirin tiknariyin]] 2006, mac anebbaḍ alibi yuweɣ (interdire) "Ussan" xef umuddu s unmugar ageragɣlan n tizlit tamaziɣt ɣ Ṭanja 2006, d issurda (accuser) ayt terabbut s ticcufert (hérésie). Immagɣ unebbaḍ asennaraf alibi d imawasen nes ɣ tegduda n tillas ad bbin iles n εabdullah εcini s uzlan n tiεεurba, sfissen agerḍ nes, deln afrak nes s waddal n uẓeddum (tinuraf : injustice), mac mmis n Cicung ur yugad ara isufa n tillas d isekraf n tinuraf. 

Mac, imakern n tifawt luḥen-d tikkelt yaḍen addal n tillas f izenẓaren n timmuzɣa, amẓen anaẓur εabdullaɣ εcini s isasan n tenzzarfut (la justice) takucamt talibit, tizi da s tesselsa talumest (accusatiɛn) n tamestagt n inig awarazerf (immigratiɛn illégale), tenkeḍ fell-as s semmus iseggasen n ugɣzu, acku ar itirir s tutlayt tamaziɣt.  

Issenta unaẓur εabdullaɣ εcini asalag n utci (grève de la faim) seg uɣzu, ḥuma ad iselkem agerḍ n tilelli i y imaran n tderfit d tenzzarfut ɣ umaḍal, iselkem awed tabrat n yan unaẓur amaziɣ anekruf ɣ tesraft n : "tagduda" "taεrabt" talibit "taɣerfant" "tanmalayt"  "tanemɣurt"

